s PC 。</p>\r\n<p>　　需要指出的是，从着手撰写到现在，文章中提到的许多内容，或许都已经发生了改变。比如 2021 年初的时候，这家搜索巨头就痛下决心，关闭了第一方的 Stadia 游戏开发工作室。</p>            </div><!--end: news_body -->\n            <div id=\"news_otherinfo\">\n                <div id=\"up_down\">\n                    <div class=\"diggit\" onclick=\"VoteNews(700631,'agree')\">\n                        <span class=\"diggnum\" id=\"digg_num_700631\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"buryit\" onclick=\"VoteNews(700631,'anti')\">\n                        <span class=\"burynum\" id=\"bury_num_700631\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                    <div id=\"digg_tip_700631\" class=\"digg_tip_detail\"> </div>\n                </div>\n                <div id=\"come_from\">\n                        来自:\n                        <a id=\"link_source2\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://hot.cnbeta.com/articles/game/1168711.htm\">cnBeta</a>\n                </div><!--end: come_from -->\n                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                <div id=\"article_A4area\">\n                    <span id=\"shareA4\" class=\"fl\">\n                        <a href=\"https://www.aliyun.com/minisite/goods?userCode=swh7dvlt\" target=\"_blank\"><b>阿里云新用户特惠，1核2G服务器87元/年</b></a>\n                    </span>\n                    <span id=\"sharebox\">\n                        <a onclick=\"PutInWz();return false;\" href=\"javascript:void(0);\">\n                            <img border=\"0\" title=\"收藏至网摘\" src=\"/Images/icon_wz.png\" alt=\"收藏\">\n                        </a>\n                        <a rel=\"nofollow\" onclick=\"ShareToTsina();return false;\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\">\n                            <img border=\"0\" title=\"转发至新浪微博\" src=\"/Images/icon_sina.gif\" alt=\"新浪微博\">\n                        </a>\n                        <a rel=\"nofollow\" onclick=\"ShareToTweixin(700631);return false;\" href=\"javascript:void(0)\">\n                            <img border=\"0\" title=\"分享至微信\" src=\"/Images/icon_weixin.gif\" alt=\"分享至微信\">\n                        </a>\n                    </span>\n                    <div class=\"clear\">\n                    </div>\n                </div><!--end: share block-->\n                <div class=\"clear\"></div>\n                <div id=\"e4\" style=\"height:60px; width:468px;\">\n                    <div id=\"div-gpt-ad-1533633736227-3\" class=\"e4-dfp\" style=\"height:60px; width:468px;\"></div>\n                </div>\n                <div id=\"news_more_info\">\n                        <div class=\"news_tags\">标签：  <a href=\"/n/tag/Google/\" class=\"catalink\">Google</a></div>\n                    <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"tagsId\" id=\"tagsId\" value=\"Google\">\n                </div>\n            </div><!--end: news_otherinfo -->\n        </div>", "tags": "Google", "url": "https://news.cnblogs.com/n/700631/", "front_image_url": ["https://img2018.cnblogs.com/news_topic/20190730073028742-506112123.png"], "praise_nums": 0, "fav_nums": 5, "comment_nums": 0, "url_object_id": "3ad99750e2db9130ec788872d74787e2", "front_image_path": "full/09bd7a9fcc3c9d378cd0e3c381f607fa5e154e26.jpg"}
